cclive (0.7.8-0.1) experimental; urgency=low

  * Non-maintainer upload.
  * New upstream release.
    + Works with libquvi 0.4. (Closes: #651638)
  * Bump build-dep on libquvi-dep to >= 0.2.16.1.
  * Add build-dep on libboost-date-time-dev.
  * Drop build-dep on cmake, use dh-autoreconf.
  * Do not set rpath when linking Boost libraries.
    + new patch: fix-rpath.diff
  * debian/watch: Also look for .tar.bz2 and .tar.xz.
  * Install NEWS as documentation and not as upstream changelog.
  * Remove debian/cclive.examples (removed upstream).
  * Use xz compression for source and binary packages.
  * debian/control: Add Vcs-* fields.
  * Bumped Standards-Version to 3.9.2 (no changes).

 -- Ansgar Burchardt <ansgar@debian.org>  Sun, 15 Jan 2012 20:13:58 +0100

